btrplace.model

Class SubMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.model.SubMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Mapping, Cloneable

    public class SubMapping
extends Object
implements Mapping
    A sub-mapping that is a limited version of a parent mapping. The scope is defined as a collection of nodes that is supposed to belong to the parent mapping. The same for the ready VMs.

    Modifications made on the mapping are automatically reported on the parent mapping. However, it is not allowed to remove a node or a VM.

    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
